### C++
# Object files
*.o
*.obj

# Precompiled Headers
*.gch
*.pch

# Dynamic libraries
*.so
*.dylib
*.dll

# Static libraries
*.a
*.lib

# Executables
*.exe
*.out

# Linker output
*.ilk
*.map
*.exp

